        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "# Incrementality Test Insights\n",
        "\n",
        "## Test Results Summary\n",
        "\n",
        "Four incrementality tests have been conducted:\n",
        "\n",
        "| Channel | Period | Type | Status |\n",
